snippet.title: The Curse of Monkey Island 3 (1997) Tribute Trailer
snippet.description:
We all love Monkey Island! Part 3 was my first game in the series and it's also the best! Never before have I experienced such a beautifully made adventure! Childhood forever :-)
#Hollywood_laesst_gruessen #monkeyisland #videogames
